{"snp4.14:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.14 ","snp4.14:0.2":"Tuvatakasutta ","snp4.14:1.1":"“Pucchami tam adiccabandhu, ","snp4.14:1.2":"Vivekam santipadanca mahesi; ","snp4.14:1.3":"Katham disva nibbati bhikkhu, ","snp4.14:1.4":"Anupadiyano lokasmim kinci”. ","snp4.14:2.1":"“Mulam papancasankhaya, ","snp4.14:2.2":"(iti bhagava) ","snp4.14:2.3":"Manta asmiti sabbamuparundhe; ","snp4.14:2.4":"Ya kaci tanha ajjhattam, ","snp4.14:2.5":"Tasam vinaya sada sato sikkhe. ","snp4.14:3.1":"Yam kinci dhammamabhijanna, ","snp4.14:3.2":"Ajjhattam atha vapi bahiddha; ","snp4.14:3.3":"Na tena thamam kubbetha, ","snp4.14:3.4":"Na hi sa nibbuti satam vutta. ","snp4.14:4.1":"Seyyo na tena manneyya, ","snp4.14:4.2":"Niceyyo atha vapi sarikkho; ","snp4.14:4.3":"Phuttho anekarupehi, ","snp4.14:4.4":"Natumanam vikappayam titthe. ","snp4.14:5.1":"Ajjhattamevupasame, ","snp4.14:5.2":"Na annato bhikkhu santimeseyya; ","snp4.14:5.3":"Ajjhattam upasantassa, ","snp4.14:5.4":"Natthi atta kuto niratta va. ","snp4.14:6.1":"Majjhe yatha samuddassa, ","snp4.14:6.2":"Umi no jayati thito hoti; ","snp4.14:6.3":"Evam thito anejassa, ","snp4.14:6.4":"Ussadam bhikkhu na kareyya kuhinci”. ","snp4.14:7.1":"“Akittayi vivatacakkhu, ","snp4.14:7.2":"Sakkhidhammam parissayavinayam; ","snp4.14:7.3":"Patipadam vadehi bhaddante, ","snp4.14:7.4":"Patimokkham atha vapi samadhim”. ","snp4.14:8.1":"“Cakkhuhi neva lolassa, ","snp4.14:8.2":"Gamakathaya avaraye sotam; ","snp4.14:8.3":"Rase ca nanugijjheyya, ","snp4.14:8.4":"Na ca mamayetha kinci lokasmim. ","snp4.14:9.1":"Phassena yada phutthassa, ","snp4.14:9.2":"Paridevam bhikkhu na kareyya kuhinci; ","snp4.14:9.3":"Bhavanca nabhijappeyya, ","snp4.14:9.4":"Bheravesu ca na sampavedheyya. ","snp4.14:10.1":"Annanamatho pananam, ","snp4.14:10.2":"Khadaniyanam athopi vatthanam; ","snp4.14:10.3":"Laddha na sannidhim kayira, ","snp4.14:10.4":"Na ca parittase tani alabhamano. ","snp4.14:11.1":"Jhayi na padalolassa, ","snp4.14:11.2":"Virame kukkucca nappamajjeyya; ","snp4.14:11.3":"Athasanesu sayanesu, ","snp4.14:11.4":"Appasaddesu bhikkhu vihareyya. ","snp4.14:12.1":"Niddam na bahulikareyya, ","snp4.14:12.2":"Jagariyam bhajeyya atapi; ","snp4.14:12.3":"Tandim mayam hassam khiddam, ","snp4.14:12.4":"Methunam vippajahe savibhusam. ","snp4.14:13.1":"Athabbanam supinam lakkhanam, ","snp4.14:13.2":"No vidahe athopi nakkhattam; ","snp4.14:13.3":"Virutanca gabbhakaranam, ","snp4.14:13.4":"Tikiccham mamako na seveyya. ","snp4.14:14.1":"Nindaya nappavedheyya, ","snp4.14:14.2":"Na unnameyya pasamsito bhikkhu; ","snp4.14:14.3":"Lobham saha macchariyena, ","snp4.14:14.4":"Kodham pesuniyanca panudeyya. ","snp4.14:15.1":"Kayavikkaye na tittheyya, ","snp4.14:15.2":"Upavadam bhikkhu na kareyya kuhinci; ","snp4.14:15.3":"Game ca nabhisajjeyya, ","snp4.14:15.4":"Labhakamya janam na lapayeyya. ","snp4.14:16.1":"Na ca katthita siya bhikkhu, ","snp4.14:16.2":"Na ca vacam payuttam bhaseyya; ","snp4.14:16.3":"Pagabbhiyam na sikkheyya, ","snp4.14:16.4":"Katham viggahikam na kathayeyya. ","snp4.14:17.1":"Mosavajje na niyetha, ","snp4.14:17.2":"Sampajano sathani na kayira; ","snp4.14:17.3":"Atha jivitena pannaya, ","snp4.14:17.4":"Silabbatena nannamatimanne. ","snp4.14:18.1":"Sutva rusito bahum vacam, ","snp4.14:18.2":"Samananam va puthujananam; ","snp4.14:18.3":"Pharusena ne na pativajja, ","snp4.14:18.4":"Na hi santo patisenikaronti. ","snp4.14:19.1":"Etanca dhammamannaya, ","snp4.14:19.2":"Vicinam bhikkhu sada sato sikkhe; ","snp4.14:19.3":"Santiti nibbutim natva, ","snp4.14:19.4":"Sasane gotamassa na pamajjeyya. ","snp4.14:20.1":"Abhibhu hi so anabhibhuto, ","snp4.14:20.2":"Sakkhidhammamanitihamadassi; ","snp4.14:20.3":"Tasma hi tassa bhagavato sasane, ","snp4.14:20.4":"Appamatto sada namassamanusikkhe”ti. ","snp4.14:20.5":"Tuvatakasuttam cuddasamam. "}